%% Diagram: Blue/green projection rebuild from the event log
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    Log[(Event log<br/>append-only)]

    subgraph Live["Currently serving reads (v1)"]
        OldProj[Projection v1 subscriber]
        OldRead[(Read model v1)]
        OldProj -->|live tail| OldRead
    end

    subgraph Rebuild["Background rebuild (v2)"]
        NewProj[Projection v2 subscriber]
        NewRead[(Read model v2)]
        NewProj -->|fold from position 0| NewRead
    end

    Log -->|tail| OldProj
    Log -->|catch-up scan, then tail| NewProj

    NewRead --> Lag{"lag(v2) &lt; SLO?"}
    Lag -->|No, keep folding| NewProj
    Lag -->|Yes| Swap[Atomically swap reader pointer to v2]
    Swap --> Drain[Let v1 drain in-flight reads]
    Drain --> Retire[Retire projection v1 + read model v1]
